reviews.text: Open bar!! Great music!! Dj spinning hottest dance mixes in town!! 19th floor inside mall!!
$148 happy hour 👍

If you come for the early happy hour you have to pay extra to stay on past 11pm for the club its about 100hkd again free drinks all night, to play darts you need to have a card if you don't have its 100hkd which you can use again and maybe other places.
They have a karaoke room,  the darts /bar room and club which opens after 11pm.
No problems with the staff drinks were averge/good usual cocktails, beers and spirits they're not stingy with the shots. Finally the security guy forgot his name black dude his a nice guy looked after me and my friends, would go back as a pre-drink place or on a weekend.
Free flow drinks
If you want a special night, search and find other options.

reviews.text: It’s a good place for dancing in Mongkok!men$350 for any free drink .its cheap!girls $100-200for any free drinks!beer ,red wine,shooters!12:00am ppl start to dancing !很喜歡這裏，因為旺角已經沒有什麼地方可以跳舞，😅已經來了很多年、三五知己自己飲酒跳舞那邊跳舞、或是中間的位置去掟標、或是可以10幾人租一間房唱K，他全層有三個地方玩樂的，只是有時候音樂不一定很好聽，但這個價錢任飲喝到飽，其實都算不錯啦⋯9:30pm-4:00am, 12點開始會有人跳舞，都很夠玩、雖然多了一些大媽但是自己跳舞也OK吧！沒有大家說得這麼差，熟客還是很多🤔我自己想來都會提早book，預約不然星期五六真的沒有位置！靚仔靚女有冇就見仁見智有時都會撞到有嘅！但呢度唔係喪溝女溝仔場囉最鍾意係咁！喜歡音樂而又鍾意跳舞嘅人就適合！而且有三個地方可以走來走去滿開心的！雖然大媽多了，但是如果自己多人來玩真的好玩！
正垃圾場。舞池只有做枚既大媽跳。侍應服務態度差，基本上吾係佢面前叫，佢地都當睇吾到你。只有上年紀既呀叔玩。 總知就吾會再去。
足夠空間感，有舒適的私人環境。
Open bar!! Great music!! Dj spinning hottest dance mixes in town!! 19th floor inside mall!!
$148 happy hour 👍
